elements.contents: public class GetPTags { public static void main(String[] args){ Document doc = Jsoup.parse(readURL("http://www.todaysgoldrate.co.intodays-gold-rate-in-pune/")); Elements p_tags = doc.select("p"); for(Element p : p_tags) { System.out.println("P tag is "+p.text()); } } public static String readURL(String url) { String fileContents = ""; String currentLine = ""; try { BufferedReader reader = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(new URL(url).openStream())); fileContents = reader.readLine(); while (currentLine != null) { currentLine = reader.readLine(); fileContents += "\n" + currentLine; } reader.close(); reader = null; } catch (Exception e) { JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(null, e.getMessage(), "Error Message", JOptionPane.OK_OPTION); e.printStackTrace(); } return fileContents; } }
